strings: Yangosh angrily picked up the sword and put it in his pocket.
<voice_0x010015BD><se_low>January: Are you slow to block? Remember when Velociraptor went extinct?
<voice_0x010015BE><se_high>Dye: Boy, boy, girl, boy, you know?
<voice_0x010015BF><se_high>Dye: It's important to relax and recover when something goes wrong. Does it make sense to enter the pie contest?
<voice_0x010015C2><se_high>Dye: It can be slow sometimes, right? Hope this doesn't mean you lose the race.
<voice_0x010015C5><se_high>Dye: But credit alone? If things fall apart, put them all together.
<voice_0x010015C6><se_high>Dye: Don't try to throw it away, or I promise to find it and bring it back.
<voice_0x010015C7><se_low>January: Press and hold to reset after repairing Lapthorn Geyser. History of Explorers
<voice_0x010015C8><se_high>Dye: So what do you do when the anger flares up?
<voice_0x010015C9><se_high>Dye: Remember that I let you go. When I'm done, I want to go back.
